tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE performance_metrics_nn_models (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    dataset_name VARCHAR(255),
    training_loss FLOAT,
    validation_loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE ModelPerformanceMetrics (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    epoch INT,
    training_loss FLOAT,
    validation_loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE ModelTrainingHistory (
    training_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    epoch INT,
    training_time INTERVAL,
    training_loss FLOAT,
    validation_loss FLOAT,
    learning_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE training_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    epoch INT,
    loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE test_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    epoch INT,
    loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
);
